jalse.actions

Class ManualActionEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • jalse.actions.ManualActionEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionEngine

    public class ManualActionEngine
extends java.lang.Object
implements ActionEngine
    A manual-tick implementation of ActionEngine. ManualActionEngine uses no additional threads and will not run any actions until resume() is called. When the engine is ticking all jobs that should be executed will be (even if past their estimated schedule time).
